Installation Instructions:
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
a) move 'colors.h' and 'conux.h' to /usr/conux
b) move 'libconux.a' to /usr/lib/conux

You will need superuser (sudo ) permissons to move this files.Create the folders
as they will not exist by default.

Once Installed you can use the library like any other standard library by giving the
preprocessor directive

#include <conux.h>


For list of functions please refer to the wiki.
